As a user(customer) 
I want to add the card
So that I can make purchase in the online shop

Scope

The add card functionality
The secutity of displaying and adding the card
Customer should be able to add Master Card and Visa Card
It should work in Chorome, Mozilla, Safari brousers
It should also works in Mobile


Pre condition:

The Customer is registered in online shop
The add card gunctionality is implemented

Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1:User can sucesfully add card
Given: User on the "My Wallet" page
When: Click on the "Add cart" button 
And:Enter valid card number/cvv/date of experience
And: Click the "Add cart" button
Then: The card is added



Scenario 2:Customer can not sucesfully add card
Given: User on the "My Wallet" page
When: Click on the "Add cart" button 
And:Enter invalid card number/cvv/date of experience
And: Click the "Add cart" button
Then: The warning message is shown








